Вакансія від 16 березня 2020
Export sales manager
20 000 грн · Rate + %
Effi
Промисловість, виробництво;
10–50 співробітників
Київ, Proviantska Street, 3.
3,7 км від центру ·
На мапі
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 2 років.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
EFFI is the Ukrainian manufacturer of ceiling water heating climate panels. The production is located in the Kharkiv region, offices located in Kyiv and Kharkiv. The company operates in the markets of Ukraine, Iceland, Denmark, Norway, Poland, Germany, Kazakhstan, and wants to develop its presence in these markets and enter new ones.Requirements:
experience in export sales is required;
knowledge of tools and techniques for effective sales;
practical experience in negotiations and presentations;
knowledge of legislation in the field of logistics and foreign economic activity;
experience in signing export contracts for the supply of goods.
Responsibilities:
customer search and acquisition (market analysis, communication with potential customers, negotiating, creating an offer, signing contracts, supporting the shipment);
work with the logistics department and a broker (paperwork, organization of supplies);
control of the transportation process, customs clearance of export goods and vehicles, providing the necessary information to foreign counterparties.
Work conditions:
Decent and stable wage (rate + % of sales);
Modern cozy and spacious office;
Opportunity for career growth and self-development;
Valuable experience in energy efficient technologies.
Send resume with photo.
